              [$a2] \amp [$b2] \amp [$c2] \amp [$d2] \\
              [$a3] \amp [$b3] \amp [$c3] \amp [$d3] \end{bmatrix}
            ```]

Use [`x\text{,}`] [`y\text{,}`] and [`z`] for the variables.

The associated linear system is:

